        "Bumi's advisor"
      ],
      "text": "Bumi's advisor was the counsel of the eccentric King Bumi. His role was to advise the king on important matters and to enforce Omashu's rules and traditions on the citizens."
    },
    {
      "body": "He was given the nickname \"Goody Two-Shoes Consul\" by Bumi. Although he was Bumi's advisor, this man was an ally of ${link_0}, the machine maker.",
