      "section": [
        "Bumi's advisor",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "He was given the nickname \"Goody Two-Shoes Consul\" by Bumi. Although he was Bumi's advisor, this man was an ally of Lian, the machine maker."
    },
    {
      "body": "The consul worked against the king and tried to prevent ${link_0} from leaving Omashu. However, ${link_1} disliked how he chose Lian over protecting the city and defeated the man singlehandedly, causing the advisor to faint.",
      "links": [
